| `pending_dues` | ₹78,100 (from 2 parties) |
| `overdue_count` | 1 (Acme Corp invoice) |
| `tds_deducted` | ₹1,000 (CA audit fees) |
| `low_stock_items` | Dell Inspiron 15, Logitech Mouse |

